{
  "texts": [
    "Then sets F of slot-fillers are linearized as follows: First, we sort the elements of F according to the sorting operator ω and obtain a sequence F of slot- fillers.",
    "Then we linearize each slot-filler in F as described above and concatenate the resulting token sequences, respecting the ordering of slot-fillers in F.Next, we describe the linearization of TIs.",
    "As TIs are represented by the content of their slots, the linearization of a TI has to include the linearization of its slots.",
    "However, a template does not impose any ordering of its slots, and hence the linearization order of the slots of a TI is undefined.",
    "Therefore, we introduce another ordering operator which orders the slots of a template."
  ]
}